overview: Adventurous director/performers Proxy Paige and Cherry Kiss travel to Belgrade, Serbia, to honor the Summer Solstice with hot, young starlets Alexis Crystal, Vyvan Hill and Misha Maver. They experience Pagan traditions, connect with nature and share lots of free-spirited sex, all chronicled in the intimate, celebratory "Solstice."
title: Solstice - A Traditionally Untraditional Adventure
